<L>__{exterior prison gate day}
<A>__{the gigantic prison gates clank open. max emerges, a tiny figure against the imposing facade. he's holding a small black valise. looks like it was made in the 40s. max looks a little less sure of himself.}
<C>__{henry}
<A>__{appears. smiling.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{i knew you could do it.}
