<D>__{i don't have a car.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{you don't have a car? what's wrong with you? you came to pick me up without a car. that's not picking a person up.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{yes, it is. i'm here. i'm picking you up.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{i don't know about this. maybe this is a mistake.}
<A>__{max turns....walks back towards the gates. starts to pound on them.}
<C>__{max }
<D>__{dave! carl!}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{max, it's okay. you're free.}
